Is the secret passage on the outside wall of Freeport ?

-----Original Message-----
From: Amanofevil@... <Amanofevil@...>
To: eq_wizards@onelist.com <eq_wizards@onelist.com>
Date: Tuesday, May 18, 1999 7:43 AM
Subject: Re: [eq_wizards] Advice *spoiler*


>From: Amanofevil@...
>
>To get to the freeport docks without facing the guards, go to w.freeport
and
>while facing the guards, head right and hug the wall. Eventually you'll
find
>a secret passage. Go through that (it can get kinda confusing) and then
>you'll eventually see some water. Go in that and then when you get out into
>the open, take a left and follow the wall. You should soon see the docks.
